metadata.description: Sugar baby takes us to another segment of our "FEVER" journey where I confide in a wealthy and privileged girl during emotional term-oil. This storyline is satire based on the "Sugar Daddy" Stereo types we are more commonly familiar with, instead this script is reversed. I explore what life would be like with this upper-hand and privilege to combat my emotional hardships and the everyday challenges, battles, and fears my self as well as many others have as a young man.
metadata.name: Sugar Baby #1
metadata.title: Sugar Baby
